Don't they make you laugh?

172
00:22:34,895 --> 00:22:37,063
I'm crazy about these horses names.

173
00:22:37,189 --> 00:22:39,523
Read there,
that one ran yesterday at Cleveland.

174
00:22:39,649 --> 00:22:42,443
Нap-py Нoo-fers.

175
00:22:43,612 --> 00:22:47,615
I'm pissing myself!
