223
00:27:09,085 --> 00:27:13,672
You bet he was warned,
then I blew off his head!

224
00:27:14,299 --> 00:27:16,800
You think of jam and bread?

225
00:27:17,427 --> 00:27:18,677
Yes!

226
00:27:18,803 --> 00:27:22,848
