228
00:27:25,185 --> 00:27:31,566
Danny, tell Pedro how I cut
that lawyer's balls off!

229
00:27:32,192 --> 00:27:35,319
The Waldorf?
Hell yes I've been to the Waldorf.

230
00:27:35,445 --> 00:27:39,823
The wouldn't let me in except
to clean the shit out their toilets!

231
00:27:43,703 --> 00:27:45,204
Watch out!

232
00:27:51,252 --> 00:27:55,255
Danny!
- Run, quickly! - Danny!

233
00:27:59,010 --> 00:28:04,598
